    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Civic federation. composed of\nII of the woman's clubs of Spokane\nwill hold It's annual meeting on Fri\nday evening. at which time the Of\nficers for the ensuing year will be\nelected. Mrs. H. c. Olney, the pres\nent president, is slated for reelection.\nwhich will be her third incumbancy.\nMrs. Olney states that she will not\nseek the Office this time, believing\nthat she has had her share of the\nhonor and is in favor Of giving place\nto some other active spirit of the\norganization."
    }
  ]
